<item>
            <title>[SPR-8017] Allow nested &lt;beans&gt; elements to be declared anywhere</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-8017</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This appears to be a schema issue since the &apos;beans&apos; element is enabled within a sequence where it would always be the last type.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
            <key id="36606">SPR-8017</key>
            <summary>Allow nested &lt;beans&gt; elements to be declared anywhere</summary>
                <type id="4" iconUrl="https://jira.spring.io/images/icons/issuetypes/improvement.png">Improvement</type>
